{"tid":1997037,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以教長輩會明白斷捨離","createTime":"2020-05-01T11:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T07:51:57.000Z","uid":225031,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c834be103789f86466d96e8693cebe6bf1fc75cc","tid":1997037,"uid":225031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"話說放假執屋竟然連阿爺年代嘅嘢仲喺度，樣樣都話有紀念價值點樣執嘢啊！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未計平時儲埋嘅膠盒同家電都已經一大堆，仲要儲勁多圖杯杯碟碟但屋企得五個人使唔使要咁多仲要係全新，完全不能理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢哋嘅解釋係爛咗嘅時候就可以換過新，但我都幾肯定佢哋係唔會記得自己有啲咁嘅嘢存在喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n執嘢嗰時我已經叫佢哋只係坐喺度睇教人地斷捨離片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我feel到佢有啲眼濕濕，搞到我都有啲心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲係咪已經患咗儲物症？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歴史系列有：三十幾年前做白事嘅衫，50幾年嘅飯<br />\n壺，三十幾年前買嘅電器仲要有單未用過......<br />\n<br />\n垃圾系列:幾袋平時買嘢嘅膠袋，鐵罐，發晒黃嘅膠盒......(其實唔係唔俾佢儲但係可唔可以唔好咁多）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說壞咗可以用嘅系列: n多全新冇用過嘅廚具(10年至30年不等),完整套裝杯碟n多套......<br />\n<br />\n啲嘢我都盡量令佢更有價值，等屋企人冇咁傷心，有啲捐左去救世軍，有啲俾人做道具，有啲搵到收藏家要咗，但屋企仍然有好多呢類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實如果唔徹底令佢哋明斷捨離，情況只會繼續<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家屋企有冇啲咁嘅長輩？點樣應對冇咁傷感情？<br />\n<br />\n第一次post咁大篇野，原諒整理得唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615d5e8f32c0da059ae71bf416625532276c0726","tid":1997037,"uid":167295,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔好話比佢哋知，Dum完佢哋唔發覺，咁嗰件野就好似從來都冇存在過係你屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b0784682af46adca9dbc9bfd52da7fc14bb8fb","tid":1997037,"uid":53530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"615d5e8f32c0da059ae71bf416625532276c0726","tid":1997037,"uid":167295,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"唔好話比佢哋知，Dum完佢哋唔發覺，咁嗰件野就好似從來都冇存在過係你屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"8060751aea5e878657ac6bde091e1e1507143187","tid":1997037,"uid":246118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6nXGvvMjCNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F